{"id":"SIPEIBOJUE3","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["<size=51>「ともに港から出撃してくれて、背中を預けてくれる味方がいて」<\/size>",1.5],["<size=51>「勝利のあとの祝宴で一緒に馬鹿騒ぎしてくれたら――」<\/size>",3],["<size=51>「敗北のあとの反省会でも慰めてくださるのでしたら」<\/size>",4.5],["<size=51>「孤独を感じる機会も少なくなるでしょう」<\/size>",6]]},{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["小さな出来事\n\n<size=45>三　戦友たち<\/size>",1]]},{"bgmDelay":2,"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"say":"母港・演習海域","bgm":"level","side":2,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"今日はここまでにしましょう","actor":404020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"あ？これで終わり？こっちの主砲はまだ十分温まってないじゃない","actor":404010,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"モチベーションがあるのは素晴らしいですが、演習海域の使用時間を過ぎています。…よもや指揮官の予定を邪魔してまでやるつもりではないでしょうね？","actor":404020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"秘書艦のシュペーもおわかりだと思いますが","actor":404020,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"うん。本当は私ももう少し戦いたかったけど、今日はここまででお願いしますね","actor":403050,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"今日はこんなに調子がいいのに…もっと長く申請すればよかったわ……","actor":404010,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"そういえば、シャルンホルスト姉妹たちとの共同訓練は毎週やっているよね。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"di